---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About </h1>
      <p>Learn more about our mission and vision</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="text-content">
         <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
<p>At MyNewBlog, we believe physics should be experienced, not just calculated. Too often, physics education gets lost in equations and formulas, forgetting the wonder and intuition that makes science truly captivating.</p>

<h2>Our Approach</h2>
<p>We strip away the complex mathematics to reveal the core concepts behind physical phenomena. Through visual explanations, thought experiments, and real-world analogies, we make physics accessible to anyone with curiosity - regardless of their mathematical background.</p>

<h2>What You'll Discover</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Physics explained through stories and analogies, not just formulas</li>
  <li>The "why" behind physical laws, not just the "how" to solve problems</li>
  <li>Historical context that shows how great minds thought about physics</li>
  <li>Practical applications that connect theory to everyday experiences</li>
</ul>

<h2>Our Promise</h2>
<p>We'll help you develop physical intuition - that gut feeling for how the universe works that transcends mathematical manipulation. Because understanding physics should feel like discovering nature's secrets, not solving math homework.</p>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Define your color variables */
  :root {
    --primary: #3b82f6;
    --secondary: #4c1d95;
    --white: #ffffff;
  }

  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary) 0%, var(--primary) 100%);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 120px 2rem 60px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .page-hero p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .page-content {
    padding: 80px 0;
  }

  .content-grid {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .text-content h2 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }

  .text-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--lab-white, #f8fafc);
  }

  .text-content ul {
    margin-left: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .text-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--lab-white, #f8fafc);
  }

  /* ðŸ”¥ MOBILE RESPONSIVE STYLES */
  /* These only activate on phones - desktop stays perfect! */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 80px 1.5rem 40px; /* Reduced padding */
    }

    .page-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem; /* Smaller heading */
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .page-hero p {
      font-size: 1.1rem; /* Smaller subtitle */
    }

    .container {
      padding: 0 1.5rem; /* Reduced side padding */
    }

    .page-content {
      padding: 60px 0; /* Reduced padding */
    }

    .content-grid {
      max-width: 100%; /* Use full width on mobile */
    }

    .text-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem; /* Smaller subheadings */
      margin: 1.5rem 0 0.8rem;
    }

    .text-content p {
      font-size: 1rem; /* Smaller body text */
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .text-content ul {
      margin-left: 1.5rem; /* Reduced indentation */
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .text-content li {
      font-size: 0.95rem; /* Smaller list items */
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }
  }

  /* Extra small phones */
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 60px 1rem 30px;
    }

    .page-hero h1 {
      font-size: 1.7rem;
    }

    .page-hero p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }

    .page-content {
      padding: 40px 0;
    }

    .text-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .text-content p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .text-content ul {
      margin-left: 1rem;
    }

    .text-content li {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  }

  /* Large desktop enhancement */
  @media (min-width: 1200px) {
    .page-hero h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    .page-hero p {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .text-content h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .text-content p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
  }
</style>